{"tha-ap126:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap126:0.2":"Sereyyavagga ","tha-ap126:0.3":"Gandhodakiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap126:1.1":"“Nisajja pasadavare, ","tha-ap126:1.2":"vipassim addasam jinam; ","tha-ap126:1.3":"Kakudham vilasantamva, ","tha-ap126:1.4":"sabbannum tamanasakam. ","tha-ap126:2.1":"Pasadassavidure ca, ","tha-ap126:2.2":"gacchati lokanayako; ","tha-ap126:2.3":"Pabha niddhavate tassa, ","tha-ap126:2.4":"yatha ca sataramsino. ","tha-ap126:3.1":"Gandhodakanca paggayha, ","tha-ap126:3.2":"buddhasettham samokirim; ","tha-ap126:3.3":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap126:3.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap126:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap126:4.2":"yam gandhodakamakirim; ","tha-ap126:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap126:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap126:5.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap126:5.2":"sugandho nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap126:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap126:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap126:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap126:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap126:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap126:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma gandhodakiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap126:8.1":"Gandhodakiyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}